member.remarks:
    The caller can utilize the information provided by this classes to instruments state machines.
    For example:

int state = 4;
for (int i = 0 ; i < 10; i++) {
    state = 6;
    if (i % 2 == 0) {
        state = 3;
    else {
        // The state varaible is guaranteed to be 6 in here.
    }
}

